                    2. Dual weild<br>
                    3. Double attack<br>
You ever try to hit some of those luclin mobs with insane Ac? Belive me its a pain in the butt. So you wan't to have as many chance to hit as possible or your going to loose agro. This is just my reasoning behind how I do it. I don't know if it made any sence or not but there it is <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  And I don't recomend going with the slower weapon. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/udvara.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dvara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 63<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/9/02 7:30:45 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm43.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=100.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Delay</span><hr size=1> Hard to answer your question Feanant. I currently use Lammy in mainhand, and Defiance in Offhand. If I find myself losing agro, &lt;sk's and monks <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  &gt; I switch out the off hand to the Praetor's blade. Yeah 8 22 kinda stinks, but that proc makes them hate me like crazy. Get blade to proc, then switch back to faster offhand weapon. Works good for me. I still belong to the school of faster = better. I know though it's different for alot of people, lvls, taunt key mashers, distance from the mob etc, all these things come into play. Veno Axe for some reason just does not make them agro me like the debuff of the Praetor's blade.<br>
